{"tid":623942,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"衛蘭肥過架摩托車？","createTime":"2018-04-10T11:35:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-10T17:55:50.000Z","uid":44121,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"19c660078105ac0838aaa86d9a3da6171b319545","tid":623942,"uid":44121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T11:35:50.000Z","msg":"同個中三學生補習<br />\n佢講咗[摩托車]<br />\n我同佢講話應該係[電單車]<br />\n佢話佢從來冇聽過呢個講法<br />\n學校老師同同學都係叫[摩托車]<br />\n然後佢堅持自己係啱<br />\n仲要笑我講[電單車]<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我已經唔想再同佢解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我想講佢哋根本就喺一個錯嘅環境長大<br />\n連自己錯都唔知 <br />\n就算想傳承廣東話都冇呢個能力<br />\n廣東話真係好快會失傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一諗到呢到就好難過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4067364a35afb3e8c34e249c6ee8f3bd374b1ef6","tid":623942,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T11:53:19.000Z","msg":"中三都唔識google <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d344a5093075675bff22c4bfca68a828072350f1","tid":623942,"uid":44121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4067364a35afb3e8c34e249c6ee8f3bd374b1ef6","tid":623942,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T11:53:19.000Z","msg":"中三都唔識google <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T11:58:29.000Z","msg":"佢哋用百度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21634209978f9d6ec788efe86d4359eed1a10369","tid":623942,"uid":12947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T17:16:13.000Z","msg":"癡撚線 咁係街或者由佢老豆老母口中應該都有聽過掛"},{"pid":"cbedf357a8becb9beaa3be83056159002ec88b13","tid":623942,"uid":19676,"like":0,